codex-codegraph adapts the CodeGraph MCP runtime for the Codex plugin surface.

This component optionally installs @colbymchenry/codegraph@1.0.1. That package
selects platform bundles for darwin, linux, and win32 on arm64 and x64. The
CodeGraph packages declare MIT license metadata.

The selected CodeGraph platform bundles may include a Node.js v24.16.0 runtime
plus vendored JavaScript dependencies and tree-sitter WASM payloads. Node.js
runtime license and bundled third-party license text is included in this
component at NODE-RUNTIME-LICENSES.md. Vendored JavaScript dependencies and WASM
payloads retain the license files included inside the selected CodeGraph
platform package under lib/node_modules/.

This NOTICE is self-contained for the marketplace plugin payload. The wider
Codex distribution also records these details in its aggregate third-party
notices.
